Package: bigDM
Type: Package
Title: Scalable Bayesian Disease Mapping Models for High-Dimensional Data
Version: 0.4.1
Date: 2022-02-01
Author: Aritz Adin [aut, cre] <aritz.adin@unavarra.es>,
        Erick Orozco-Acosta [aut] <erick.orozco@unavarra.es>,
        Maria Dolores Ugarte [aut] <lola@unavarra.es>
Maintainer: Aritz Adin <aritz.adin@unavarra.es>
Description: This package includes functions to fit scalable disease mapping models for high-dimensional spatial and spatio-temporal count data using the INLA technique for approximate Bayesian inference in latent Gaussian models.
URL: https://github.com/spatialstatisticsupna/bigDM
BugReports: https://github.com/spatialstatisticsupna/bigDM/issues
